DyCoNet is a Gephi plugin that can be used to identify dynamic communities in networks. To add DyCoNet to an existing Gephi installation:
1. Download DyCoNet.nbm.
2. Open Gephi.
3. Go to the menu Tools > Plugins > Downloaded.
4. Click on Add Plugins..., and select DyCoNet.nbm.
5. Click on Install and follow the installation wizard.